folder: Stone Avenue & Somers Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1)
Stone Ave., east side, between Somers at left, and Truxton Streets. A view of W. J. Davis home, built in 1869 standing in 1908. In 1900 it
was the 23rd Assembly District Republican Club.

1900.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
Same, showing the south side.
1900.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3)
The same, another view.
April 20, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
